---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
// Squelette de CGV. BLOQUANT : relecture par un professionnel du droit avant
// la première vente (architecture v2, section 9). Régime TVA à valider avec
// le comptable (voir site/donnees-legales.md).
---

<Base
  title="Terms of sale — zeurion.ai"
  description="Terms of sale for the Zeurion sponsor prospecting report."
>
  <main class="container">
    <p class="mono eyebrow"><a href="/">← zeurion.ai</a></p>
    <h1>Terms of sale</h1>
    <p class="draft mono">[DRAFT : pending legal review, not yet in force]</p>

    <h2>1. Service</h2>
    <p>
      Zeurion provides a one-time sponsor prospecting report prepared for a single
      newsletter, as described on the order page: matched brands with sourced evidence,
      contact identification with sources and email status, pitch drafts, a pricing
      recommendation, and a summary media kit. The service is provided by Agence Wengraf
      SASU (see the Legal notice) and is intended for business customers (B2B).
    </p>

    <h2>2. Price and payment</h2>
    <p>
      The price is displayed at checkout and paid in full at order via our payment
      provider (Stripe). VAT treatment depends on the customer's country and status:
      reverse charge may apply for EU businesses; French VAT applies where required.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Delivery</h2>
    <p>
      The report is delivered by email within 5 business days of receiving the completed
      intake form. If we consider the newsletter is not a fit for the method (for example,
      an audience too general or too small for direct sponsorship sales), we say so and
      refund in full before starting the work.
    </p>

    <h2>4. What we do not promise</h2>
    <p>
      We do not guarantee commercial outcomes (closed sponsorships or revenue). We
      guarantee the documented nature of the report: factual claims are sourced and dated,
      and unverified contact details are marked as such. Contact data decays; the report
      reflects public information at the date of research.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Data and conduct</h2>
    <p>
      Reports are built from publicly available information only. The customer remains
      solely responsible for their own outreach and its compliance with applicable
      anti-spam and data protection laws.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Governing law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by French law. [TO COMPLETE : juridiction, médiation le cas échéant, après relecture juridique.]</p>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  main { padding-top: 3.5rem; max-width: 720px; }
  .eyebrow { font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .eyebrow a { text-decoration: none; }
  .draft { color: var(--accent); font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  h2 { margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  p { color: var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
</style>
